      <name>rivenmedia/riven</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/compare/v0.21.21...v0.22.0"&gt;0.22.0&lt;/a&gt; (2025-08-05)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add TorBox downloader to Riven (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/issues/1074"&gt;#1074&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/9875109e25c3c67cc3cdcd2cd450547dce365854"&gt;9875109&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add TRAKT_API_CLIENT_ID env to override the default trakt client id used by trakt indexer (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/7fd087f7b46cde4b6542f1d57ca394a1b4bf28ca"&gt;7fd087f&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;set the media type when performing search (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/issues/1110"&gt;#1110&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/16ada643305024ac3e1b3b7f8defc1faef6aa77e"&gt;16ada64&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;fixed hanging on downloader. improved logging. (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/issues/1116"&gt;#1116&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/422db783e1a3f07262601478841d9576d70cb332"&gt;422db78&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;handle create_item_from_imdb_id response exception (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/d91dd254c08fbb410706d4fc6cb97f3691ebc67c"&gt;d91dd25&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;readtimeout issue with rd, updated timeout to 25s instead of 15s. added exception handling for this as well. (&lt;a href="https://github.com/rivenmedia/riven/commit/45105dbd70854d70c56f4ebec3d6ca6ea7ef1504"&gt;45105db&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
